  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/54f425f0776a3e5ee5abcb3f616dfdab.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/54f425f0776a3e5ee5abcb3f616dfdab.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny is starting her shift at The Lucky Rabbit Casino when the Cool Cats, a local gang, invade and start stealing all the cocktail cherries! Chase them down across 10 exciting levels all over Starlight City! From a magic show to an underwater martini club to a relaxing Japanese garden, explore the venues Starlight City as to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/b49a17e77dd793e3201429e0de1d3a1e.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/b49a17e77dd793e3201429e0de1d3a1e.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=429 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny's ears have many uses! Platform across levels by grabbing walls, boxes and objects. Quickly grab cherries and health items with a spin. Grab enemy projectiles and throw them back! Some projectiles can be parried back at enemies or stopped in their track. Give it a spin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny can also use her ears to grab and throw useful items, such as keys, dynamite and ninja stars. Each item is unique and can be used to fight enemies or solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/1fc12e1daa82d41e8fbae77dc39ea0aa.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/1fc12e1daa82d41e8fbae77dc39ea0aa.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=395 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level has its own theme!  Collect a sweet treat to restore health or a signature cocktail for temporary invincibility. Level specific items can help solve puzzles. For example, Magnus' magic crystal ball reveals safe paths and hidden rooms filled with goodies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The final game will have 10 levels that are currently in progress and are available to play through Early Access on Steam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/848a1ef0d13531624ce99fed68226993.apng?t=1772015101\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/848a1ef0d13531624ce99fed68226993.poster.avif?t=1772015101\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/54f425f0776a3e5ee5abcb3f616dfdab.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/54f425f0776a3e5ee5abcb3f616dfdab.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny is starting her shift at The Lucky Rabbit Casino when the Cool Cats, a local gang, invade and start stealing all the cocktail cherries! Chase them down across 10 exciting levels all over Starlight City! From a magic show to an underwater martini club to a relaxing Japanese garden, explore the venues Starlight City as to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/b49a17e77dd793e3201429e0de1d3a1e.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/b49a17e77dd793e3201429e0de1d3a1e.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=429 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny's ears have many uses! Platform across levels by grabbing walls, boxes and objects. Quickly grab cherries and health items with a spin. Grab enemy projectiles and throw them back! Some projectiles can be parried back at enemies or stopped in their track. Give it a spin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Honey Bunny can also use her ears to grab and throw useful items, such as keys, dynamite and ninja stars. Each item is unique and can be used to fight enemies or solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/1fc12e1daa82d41e8fbae77dc39ea0aa.avif?t=1772015101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras_big/1fc12e1daa82d41e8fbae77dc39ea0aa.webp?t=1772015101 width=1560 height=395 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level has its own theme!  Collect a sweet treat to restore health or a signature cocktail for temporary invincibility. Level specific items can help solve puzzles. For example, Magnus' magic crystal ball reveals safe paths and hidden rooms filled with goodies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The final game will have 10 levels that are currently in progress and are available to play through Early Access on Steam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/848a1ef0d13531624ce99fed68226993.apng?t=1772015101\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641550/extras/848a1ef0d13531624ce99fed68226993.poster.avif?t=1772015101\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span></p>",
